column5: Well we headed out hoping for pike or crappie to start.. no pike to speak of but one nice crappie after many hours waiting. Nautifish said to give my best smile, so I gave a smile that screams "I'mmm HAAANNNDSSOMMMMEEE"    After that it was slow.. just 3 small perch between the two of us but oh well better than being at home all day. I also got a sweet new hat, I think it was good luck!

Yup not too much biteing today. The wind was just wicked cold too..Brrrrr  Rich caught a nice crappie as you can see plus a perch me i caught two perch in about four hrs.....lol  Ohh well thats fishin.....
I like the AC DC hat.Great Band. thanks for the picture of the little critter .Best of all no skunk Rich.
You look like ur constipated rich.
Yes he does Nautifish or he was trying to pass wind.
I am the man of 1000 faces!
